<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٨٦٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3909">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ مُرَّةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6088">مَسْرُوقٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا تُقْتَلُ نَفْسٌ إِلَّا كَانَ عَلَى ابْنِ آدَمَ الْأَوَّلِ كِفْلٌ مِنْهَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>